# HireTrack frontend environment.
# Copy to `.env.local` for local overrides (optional).
#
# In development this is left UNSET: requests go to `/api`, which the Vite dev
# server proxies to Django on :8000 (see vite.config.ts).
#
# In production (Vercel) set VITE_API_URL to the deployed Render API base,
# INCLUDING the /api suffix and NO trailing slash, e.g.:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://hiretrack-api.onrender.com/api
VITE_API_URL=
